videos.description: Texas Tech is making a habit of storming the court, this time after stopping No. 3 Oklahoma in the final seconds to pull off the upset.
videos.headline: Another Texas Tech upset, another Texas Tech court storming

videos.description: Texas Tech coach Tubby Smith talks about how proud he is of his team, the difference maker in the Red Raiders' 65-63 upset win over the Sooners and how thrilled he is to give fans the win "they wanted so bad."
videos.headline: Tubby Smith on upset: 'It's really exciting for these kids'
